---

<Layout 
  title="RHworks | 氷堂リョージ - 漫画家"
  description="漫画家・氷堂リョージの公式サイト。作品紹介、プロフィール、最新情報をお届けします。"
>
	<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 py-20">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
		<header class="mb-24 text-center md:text-left">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-pink-accent bg-brand-pink/30 rounded-full uppercase mb-8">
        Manga Artist / Illustrator
      </div>
			<h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-serif font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6 transition-all duration-700">
				RHworks
			</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-gray/80 font-serif italic mb-10">
        "Crafting Stories, Delivering Trust, Embracing Challenges."
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start gap-4">
        {snsLinks.map(link => (
          <a 
            href={link.url} 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label={link.name}
            class="group w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-brand-surface border border-brand-pink/40 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:border-brand-pink transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:scale-110 p-1"
          >
            {link.name === 'X' ? (
              <div class="w-full h-full bg-brand-pink-accent rounded-full p-2.5 flex items-center justify-center">
                <img 
                  src={link.icon} 
                  alt={link.name} 
                  class="w-full h-full object-contain opacity-100"
                />
              </div>
            ) : (
              <img 
                src={link.icon} 
                alt={link.name} 
                class="w-full h-full object-contain opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
              />
            )}
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
		</header>

    <!-- Content Sections -->
    <div class="space-y-32">
      <!-- About -->
      <section id="about" class="space-y-8" x-data="{ lang: 'jp' }">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-brand-pink-accent/80">Profile</h2>
          <div class="flex p-0.5 bg-brand-pink/10 rounded-full">
            <button 
              @click="lang = 'jp'" 
              class="px-4 py-1.5 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest rounded-full transition-all"
              :class="lang === 'jp' ? 'bg-white text-brand-pink-accent shadow-sm' : 'text-brand-gray/50 hover:text-brand-pink-accent'"
            >JP</button>
            <button 
              @click="lang = 'en'" 
              class="px-4 py-1.5 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest rounded-full transition-all"
              :class="lang === 'en' ? 'bg-white text-brand-pink-accent shadow-sm' : 'text-brand-gray/50 hover:text-brand-pink-accent'"
            >EN</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none text-brand-gray/90 leading-relaxed font-serif text-lg">
          <div x-show="lang === 'jp'" x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-300" x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 translate-y-2" x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0">
            <p class="mb-4">
              <strong class="text-gray-900 text-2xl block mb-4 italic">氷堂リョージ (Ryoji Hido)</strong>
              日本の漫画家。<br />
              氷堂涼二（ひどうりょうじ）名義と、氷堂リョージ名義の著書があります。<br />
              中学生から同人時代にも使っていたペンネームだったことと、まんがくらぶで４コマ誌デビューした折に「より大衆向けにしたい」という発想で氷堂リョージに替えました。以降の著書はリョージ名義です。
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">
              また、一部の商業誌で紙版を出版できないタイトルを「著者制作版」としてKDPオンデマンド出版しています。少女マンガ、４コママンガ、エッセイマンガ、イラスト本など多岐にわたるジャンルを手掛けています。
            </p>
            <p>
              禅宗系の中高出身のご縁で曹洞宗からの出版物もあります。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div x-show="lang === 'en'" x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-300" x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 translate-y-2" x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0" class="text-base">
            <p class="mb-4">
               <strong class="text-gray-900 text-2xl block mb-4 italic">Ryoji Hido (氷堂リョージ)</strong>
               Ryoji Hido is a Japanese manga artist who publishes under two pen names: Ryoji Hido (氷堂涼二) and Ryoji Hido (氷堂リョージ). The latter name, which he had been using since his middle school days and throughout his doujinshi period, was officially adopted when he debuted in the 4-panel manga magazine Manga Club. He chose this name to appeal to a broader audience, and has since used it for all subsequent publications.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Hido works across various genres including shoujo manga, 4-panel comics, essay manga, and illustration books. Some of his works that couldn’t be published in print through traditional commercial magazines are now available as “author-produced editions” via KDP (Kindle Direct Publishing).
            </p>
            <p>
              With a background in Zen Buddhism from his middle and high school years, Hido has also contributed to publications from the Soto Zen school of Buddhism.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Works -->
      <section id="works" class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <h2 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-brand-pink-accent/80">Selected Works</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div x-data="{ open: false }" class="relative">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6" :class="open ? '' : 'max-h-[640px] overflow-hidden'">
            {works.map(work => (
              <a 
                href={work.url} 
                target="_blank" 
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="group flex flex-col h-full bg-brand-surface/30 border border-brand-pink/10 rounded-2xl p-3 hover:bg-white hover:border-brand-pink/40 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500"
              >
                <div class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-xl bg-brand-pink/5 mb-3 overflow-hidden relative border border-brand-pink/5 shadow-inner">
                  {work.image ? (
                    <>
                      <img 
                        src={`/images/thumbnails/${work.image}`} 
                        alt={work.title} 
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale brightness-125 transition-all duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:brightness-100" 
                      />
                      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-pink-accent/60 mix-blend-multiply group-hover:opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-pink/30 group-hover:opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                      <div class="absolute inset-0 border-[6px] border-brand-beige group-hover:border-transparent transition-all duration-500 rounded-xl"></div>
                    </>
                  ) : (
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center p-4">
                      <div class="w-full h-full border-[1px] border-brand-pink/20 rounded shadow-sm bg-white/50 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <span class="text-[10px] text-brand-pink-accent font-serif tracking-tighter opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">RHworks</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  )}
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-[11px] font-bold text-brand-gray/90 leading-tight line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-brand-pink-accent transition-colors mb-1">
                  {work.title}
                </h3>
                <span class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-gray/40 font-bold mt-auto pt-2">{work.label || 'Amazon'} →</span>
              </a>
            ))}
            <div x-show="!open" class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-beige via-brand-beige/80 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
          </div>
          
          <button 
            @click="open = !open" 
            class="mt-8 w-full py-4 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase border border-brand-pink/20 hover:bg-brand-pink/5 hover:border-brand-pink/40 transition-all rounded-full text-brand-pink-accent bg-brand-beige/50 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-sm"
          >
            <span x-text={`open ? 'Minimize Collection' : 'Expand Full Library (${works.length} titles)'`}></span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- YouTube Videos -->
      <section id="videos" class="space-y-12">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-brand-pink-accent/80">Featured Videos</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          {[
            { id: 't-rm55DtVxA', title: '「虫の皇女マユの旅」完結記念・読者プレゼント動画' },
            { id: 'CHuxTm6zLvg', title: 'αβlabプロモテストムービー' }
          ].map(video => (
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="group relative bg-brand-surface p-1.5 rounded-[2rem] border border-brand-pink/30 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden">
                <div class="aspect-video rounded-[1.75rem] overflow-hidden bg-gray-200 relative">
                  <iframe 
                    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"
                    src={`https://www.youtube.com/embed/${video.id}`}
                    title={video.title}
                    frameborder="0" 
                    allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
                    referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" 
                    allowfullscreen
                  ></iframe>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute top-4 right-6 flex gap-1.5 opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-pink-accent"></div>
                  <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-pink"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs font-serif italic text-brand-gray/60 px-4">
                {video.title}
              </p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- AI Stance -->
      <section id="ai-stance" x-data="{ expanded: false }" class="p-10 bg-brand-surface rounded-[3rem] space-y-6 border border-brand-pink/10 relative overflow-hidden group transition-all duration-500">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-pink/10 rounded-full -mr-16 -mt-16 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125"></div>
        <h2 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-brand-pink-accent/80 flex items-center">
          My Stance on AI
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-brand-gray font-serif leading-relaxed relative z-10">
          <p class="text-lg font-bold">
            「どのような技術を使っても、最終的な表現を決めるのは人間の個性と判断である」
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-brand-gray/80">
            漫画家・作家として、私は制作プロセスにおける生成AI（機械学習技術）の利用について、透明性を保ちつつ、技術の可能性を広げていく姿勢をとっています。
          </p>
          
          <div x-show="expanded" x-collapse>
            <div class="space-y-6 pt-4 border-t border-brand-pink/20 mt-6">
              <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-brand-gray/80 leading-relaxed">
                <div class="space-y-4">
                  <p>私の創作活動は、かつての「無断転載（右クリック）禁止」論争から始まり、インターネットとの関係の変化を経て、現在は生成AIなどの新しい技術も視野に入れながら創作を続けています。</p>
                  <p>技術による学習やデータ活用には不可逆的な側面があり、かつて抵抗を覚えた時期もありました。しかし今では、「どのような技術を使っても、最終的な表現を決めるのは人間の個性と判断である」という考えに至っています。これは、技術を盲目的に肯定する立場ではなく、人間の創造性を中心に据えた上で、必要なものを選び取る姿勢です。</p>
                  <p>インターネットとともに積み重ねてきた経験が、新しい技術の登場によって“さらに広い可能性”を得たと実感しています。同時に、利用する技術についてはできる限り透明性を保ち、コミックスの後書きなどで使用ツールを明記するようにしています。創作に関わる技術を記録し共有することは、開発者や未来のクリエイターがより良い表現へ進む足場になると考えるからです。</p>
                  <p>私は今後も、多様なツールを適切に選び、人間の表現として責任を持てる形で活用し、創作を続けていくつもりです。これが、私の「生成AIに対するスタンス」です。</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="pt-6 border-t border-brand-pink/10 space-y-4">
                  <h4 class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-pink-accent">My Stance on Generative AI</h4>
                  <p>My creative journey began in the era of “no unauthorized reproduction” and “right-click prohibition,” and over time my relationship with the internet has changed significantly. Today, I continue my work while also exploring new tools, including generative AI.</p>
                  <p>There was a time when I felt uneasy about the irreversible nature of data collection and machine learning. But I have come to believe that regardless of the tools involved, the final shape of a work is determined by human judgment and individuality. This does not mean embracing technology blindly; rather, it reflects a commitment to keeping human creativity at the center while choosing the tools that serve it best.</p>
                  <p>The experiences I’ve built alongside the evolution of the internet now feel expanded by the arrival of new technologies. At the same time, I try to maintain transparency in my process and disclose the tools I use—such as in the afterwords of my comics—because I believe that documenting and sharing our methods helps future creators and developers build on firmer ground.</p>
                  <p>Going forward, I intend to continue selecting and using a variety of tools responsibly, in ways that I can stand behind as a human creator. This is my stance on generative AI.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <button 
            @click="expanded = !expanded" 
            class="text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-pink-accent hover:text-brand-gray transition-colors flex items-center border-b border-brand-pink-accent/30 pb-1"
          >
            <span x-text="expanded ? 'Read Less' : 'Read Full Statement'"></span>
            <svg x-show="!expanded" class="w-3 h-3 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
            <svg x-show="expanded" class="w-3 h-3 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 15l7-7 7 7"></path></svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Bottom Navigation / Contact -->
      <section class="pt-24 pb-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 border-t border-brand-pink/10">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-brand-pink-accent/80">Contact</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray/70 text-sm italic leading-relaxed">
            制作のご依頼や、作品に関するお問い合わせはこちらまで。<br>
            For project inquiries or collaborations.
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:ryojihido@gmail.com" class="inline-block px-12 py-5 bg-brand-gray text-brand-beige rounded-2xl font-bold hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">
            Email Me
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-brand-pink-accent/80">Location</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray/70 text-sm font-serif italic">Kanagawa, Japan</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="mt-40 pt-16 border-t border-brand-pink/20 text-center">
      <p class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.5em] text-brand-gray/40 uppercase">
        &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} RHworks Ryoji Hido
      </p>
    </footer>
	</main>
  
  <script is:inline src="https://unpkg.com/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js"></script>
</Layout>
